      <div class="v2-what-is-iris__label-{{ section.id }}" style="display:block;margin-bottom:3.2rem;">IV — The reveal</div>
      <h2 class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-title-{{ section.id }}">
        It is not shown.<br>
        <em>Until it is yours.</em>
      </h2>
      <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-rule-{{ section.id }}"></div>
      <p class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-body-{{ section.id }}">
        IRIS is assigned before purchase, but hidden until activation. You do not choose your exact piece in advance.
        Ownership is part of the reveal. The work becomes fully known only when it belongs to you.
      </p>

      <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-steps-{{ section.id }}">
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-step-{{ section.id }}">
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-num-{{ section.id }}">01</div>
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-step-title-{{ section.id }}">You purchase</div>
          <p>Your piece is sealed. Its identity is assigned — but invisible. You receive a numbered, sealed IRIS delivered to your door.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-step-{{ section.id }} v2-what-is-iris__reveal-step-{{ section.id }}--highlight">
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-num-{{ section.id }}">02</div>
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-step-title-{{ section.id }}">You scan</div>
          <p>Hold your phone to the NFC chip. In that single moment — artwork, number, rarity, archive entry. Everything at once. This is the moment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-step-{{ section.id }}">
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-num-{{ section.id }}">03</div>
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__reveal-step-title-{{ section.id }}">It is yours</div>
          <p>Your piece enters the permanent archive under your name. Its record cannot be altered. The number belongs to you — and only to you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="v2-what-is-iris__aesthetics-{{ section.id }}">
      <div class="v2-what-is-iris__aesthetics-left-{{ section.id }}">
        <span class="v2-what-is-iris__label-{{ section.id }}">V — The format</span>
        <h2 class="v2-what-is-iris__aesthetics-title-{{ section.id }}">An art object.<br>Not a<br><span class="v2-what-is-iris__gold-em-{{ section.id }}">commodity.</span></h2>
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__aesthetics-copy-{{ section.id }}">
          <p>IRIS exists at the intersection of contemporary art, material craft, and collected value. Each edition is built around a body of work — a specific artist, a specific vision, a specific moment in time.</p>
          <p>The format is fixed. The 4 x 4 frame, the archival paper, the embedded gold — these are constants. What changes is the artwork inside. Every edition is different. Every piece within an edition is numbered.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="v2-what-is-iris__aesthetics-thoughts-{{ section.id }}">
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__thought-{{ section.id }}">
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__thought-marker-{{ section.id }}">Thought 01</div>
          <p>The object is small, but the system behind it is large. It can live on a desk, on a wall, in a safe, in an archive.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__thought-{{ section.id }}">
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__thought-marker-{{ section.id }}">Thought 02</div>
          <p>The gold inside is not decorative. It is <em>weight</em> — a real material anchoring the work to something beyond aesthetic. You feel it when you hold it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-{{ section.id }}">
      <div class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-header-{{ section.id }}">
        <span class="v2-what-is-iris__label-{{ section.id }}">VI — The platform</span>
        <h2 class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-title-{{ section.id }}">IRIS is a format.<br><span class="v2-what-is-iris__gold-em-{{ section.id }}">Any artist can use it.</span></h2>
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-copy-{{ section.id }}">
          <p>The IRIS object — the format, the gold, the NFC, the archive — is a platform. Artists, galleries, studios, and brands can launch their own IRIS edition. The infrastructure is ours. The artwork is theirs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-grid-{{ section.id }}">
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-card-{{ section.id }} v2-what-is-iris__collab-card-{{ section.id }}--featured">
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-icon-{{ section.id }}">✦</div>
          <h3>Artists</h3>
          <p>Launch a numbered collectible edition without building fulfillment, archive, pricing, or activation systems from scratch.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-card-{{ section.id }}">
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-icon-{{ section.id }}">◌</div>
