          <p>Translate a show into a collectible edition with a clear structure, a permanent archive, and built-in ownership mechanics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-card-{{ section.id }}">
          <div class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-icon-{{ section.id }}">⌘</div>
          <h3>Studios & Brands</h3>
          <p>Create limited physical editions that merge object, identity, and permanence in a format that already works.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-cta-{{ section.id }}">
        <a href="/pages/collaborate" class="v2-what-is-iris__button-gold-{{ section.id }}">Start your edition →</a>
        <div class="v2-what-is-iris__collab-note-{{ section.id }}">Applications reviewed within 48 hours. No upfront cost for public editions.</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="v2-what-is-iris__closing-{{ section.id }}">
      <h2 class="v2-what-is-iris__closing-title-{{ section.id }}">A piece of art.<br>A gram of gold.<br><em>A number that is yours.</em></h2>
      <p class="v2-what-is-iris__closing-copy-{{ section.id }}">IRIS is not one thing. It is an object, a system, a record, and a reveal. It becomes complete only when it is owned.</p>
      <a href="/products/iris-the-unseen-edition" class="v2-what-is-iris__button-gold-{{ section.id }}">Shop IRIS →</a>
    </section>

    <div class="v2-what-is-iris__ticker-{{ section.id }}">
      <div class="v2-what-is-iris__ticker-inner-{{ section.id }}">
